                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman,</hi> 112 <hi rend="italic">G.</hi>) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's conviction in the name of Carpenter—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted at Clerkenwell, May,</hi> 1850, <hi rend="italic">confined Six Months</hi>)—I was present—he is the person.</p>
